name: AS_GCM_BOL_SHOW_FILLIN_ACCESS_INFO_TOGGLE
description: Provides a workflow that shows users why the Complete fill-ins action for clauses in the clause set summary is or is not available. Set false to not show this workflow, and set true if you do want to show this page when selecting Complete fill-ins. If true, "Complete fill-ins" is clickable even if it is not available.
